title: 1-METRE WIDE SINK HOLE APPEARS IN MIDDLE OF ANG MO KIO AVE 5
text:
1-METRE WIDE SINK HOLE APPEARS IN MIDDLE OF ANG MO KIO AVE 5   Sat, 18/02/2017 - 10:32am 
A 1 metre wide sinkhole appeared in the middle of the road along Ang Mo Kio Ave 5 at around 5.30 pm yesterday. The sinkhole appeared as PUB was undergoing water pipe laying operations in the centre lane of Ang Mo Kio Ave 5. 
The sinkhole was cordoned off by workers with orange cones and PUB's contractor was activated to fill up the sinkhole. Road repairs are expected to be completed by this morning. Editor's Note:
